One character per account on the server should fix the farming issues that other servers have... How much can one character on the server farm? I have always been against farming on other servers, but I see on FV where farming really wouldn't be a big problme. I have several personal friends that will not come to Firiona Vie because of the TLC, and they are excellent RPers. I feel that FV is missing out on some of the best RPers simply because of the TLC and I would like to see it removed. Just keep it at 1 character per account, and keep all the language, grouping, rules the same and get rid of the TLC!!!<br>
